{{#extend "layout"}}
  {{#content "main"}}
    <div class="container mx-auto px-4 py-8">
      <div class="prose max-w-3xl mx-auto">
        <h1 class="text-4xl font-bold mb-8">About</h1>               

        <!-- Template Information -->
        <div class="card bg-base-100 shadow-lg mb-8">
          <div class="card-body">
            <h2 class="card-title">Build Your Own Directory</h2>
            <p>This directory platform is powered by <a href="https://codehooks.io">Codehooks.io</a>, offering a complete boilerplate template to create your own directory service. Whether you're building a business directory, resource listing, or community platform, our template provides the perfect foundation.</p>
            
            <h3 class="text-xl font-semibold mt-4">Key Features</h3>
            <ul class="list-disc ml-6 mt-2">
              <li>Ready-to-use backend powered by Codehooks.io serverless infrastructure</li>
              <li>Modern, responsive frontend design</li>
              <li>Built-in search and filtering capabilities</li>
              <li>User authentication and management</li>
              <li>Customizable categories and fields</li>
              <li>Easy deployment process</li>
            </ul>

            <h3 class="text-xl font-semibold mt-4">Getting Started</h3>
            <p>Create your own directory service in minutes:</p>
            <ol class="list-decimal ml-6 mt-2">
              <li>Clone the <a href="https://github.com/RestDB/directory-template">template repository</a></li>
              <li>Set up your Codehooks.io account</li>
              <li>Configure your environment variables</li>
              <li>Customize categories and fields</li>
              <li>Deploy your service</li>
            </ol>

            <p class="mt-4">Start building your directory service today with our battle-tested template!</p>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  {{/content}}
{{/extend}} 